    "The feature extraction module f fe (⋅) aims to extract informative latent features from the input.",
    "The prediction module f p (⋅) aims to model the mapping from extracted features to the wind power output.",
    "Therefore, the entire process including the feature engineering to the prediction can be expressed by Eqs.",
    "(15) and (16), where z is the input of the feature engineering module.",
    "It can be either the original input x or the subseries s."
